---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Code of Conduct | Smite Club">
  <style>
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f9ff 0%, #e0f2fe 100%);
      padding: 60px 0;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #7dd3fc;
    }
    
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 36px;
      color: #0a0a1a;
    }
    
    .section {
      padding: 50px 0;
    }
    
    .content {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .content h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #0a0a1a;
      margin: 30px 0 15px;
    }
    
    .content p {
      color: #475569;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    
    .content ul {
      color: #475569;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding-left: 25px;
    }
    
    .content li {
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
  </style>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Code of Conduct</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content">
        <p>Smite Club events are built on competition, community, and respect. This code ensures everyone has a great experience.</p>
        
        <h2>Sportsmanship</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Play fair. Know your rules and army.</li>
          <li>Be gracious in victory and defeat.</li>
          <li>Help new players learn — we all started somewhere.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Respect</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Treat all players, judges, and staff with respect.</li>
          <li>No harassment, discrimination, or toxic behavior.</li>
          <li>Keep language appropriate for all ages.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Integrity</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Use correct list submissions. No late changes.</li>
          <li>Accurate measurements and clear dice rolling.</li>
          <li>Questionable play? Call a judge. Don't argue — clarify.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Property</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Don't touch other players' models without permission.</li>
          <li>Keep the venue clean. Pick up your space.</li>
          <li>Report damage immediately to staff.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Enforcement</h2>
        <p>Judges and staff can issue warnings, remove players from games, or eject players from the event for violations. Serious violations may result in bans from future events.</p>
        
        <p style="margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">
          <strong>Questions or concerns?</strong> Email <a href="mailto:info@smiteclub40k.com" style="color: #0ea5e9;">info@smiteclub40k.com</a> or speak to any judge at the event.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
